timeline.body:
Two possible strategies to reduce the nesting here:
1. Negate all of the conditions, and "return early," e.g.:
```java
if (!currentCondition) {
    return;
}
// This code is now left by four columns
```
2. Add a helper method, where you can perform all of these checks in one place.
```java
if (!validUpdate(...)) {
    return;
}
// This code is now left by 4 * k columns
```

